# Canonical host: https://anvo.io
# Anything arriving via the Cloudflare-Pages default URL (*.pages.dev) or
# www. is 301'd to the apex. `:splat` preserves the path, `!` forces the
# redirect over any filesystem match.
https://anvo-website.pages.dev/*   https://anvo.io/:splat   301!
https://*.anvo-website.pages.dev/* https://anvo.io/:splat   301!
https://www.anvo.io/*              https://anvo.io/:splat   301!
